OL,6,FThe family of IRA man Michael Kearney
OL,7,Fwho was murdered by the terror group's
OL,8,Fnow notorious internal security unit
OL,9,Fhave been told he ''could and should''
OL,10,Fhave been saved.
OL,12,FThe 20-year-old republican from west
OL,13,FBelfast was abducted in the summer of
OL,14,F1979, interrogated, then shot in the
OL,15,Fhead, his body dumped close to the
OL,16,Fborder.
OL,18,FA terrible end given to those accused
OL,19,Fof being informers.
