OL,6,FAt the height of the troubles, he was
OL,7,Fin charge of the IRA's internal
OL,8,Fsecurity unit which was nicknamed the
OL,9,Fnutting squad.
OL,11,FIt is understood the Kenova
OL,12,Finvestigation has linked him either
OL,13,Fdirectly or indirectly to 14 murders.
OL,15,FThe army, MI5, police and the IRA,
OL,16,Fhave also come under scrutiny.
