OL,3,CFamily of murdered IRA man told police
OL,4,Cand army 'could' have prevented killing
OL,6,FIn relation to the murder of Michael
OL,7,FKearney, his brother Seamus, who was
OL,8,Falso in the IRA, said in a statement:
OL,9,F''We have been informed by the
OL,10,FOperation Kenova team that Michael's
OL,11,Flife could and should have been saved
OL,12,Fby those in authority.
OL,14,F''On at least 3 separate occasions the
OL,15,Fmilitary and RUC Special Branch were
OL,16,Finformed by at least two agents
OL,17,Fholding Michael that he was in grave
OL,18,Fdanger and had arrived in the Irish
OL,19,Frepublic to be shot dead. They failed
OL,20,Fto act.
