OL,6,F''Crucially, their first agent report
OL,7,Fwas on June 27th 1979, two days after
OL,8,FMichael was handed over to the
OL,9,Finfiltrated unit known as 'IRA
OL,10,Finternal Security' highlighting that
OL,11,FMichael would be shot dead.''
OL,13,FSolicitor Kevin Winters who represents
OL,14,Fa number of families said: "No effort
OL,15,Fwas made to intervene and save that
OL,16,Fyoung mans life, intelligence was
OL,17,Faccessed at all costs and if people
OL,18,Fdied at collateral damage, well then
OL,19,Fthat's the horrible takeaway point.
